  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<em>You cause your rivals to spend additional precious resources while wounded.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Int 13, Use Magic Device 5 ranks.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>As a full-round action, you can curse a creature you've dealt damage to since the beginning of your last round to use certain powers quickly. The creature must succeed at a Fortitude save or if it uses any of the following class abilities during the next minute, it must spend at least two daily uses or rounds of that ability: arcane pool, arcane reservoir, bardic performance, bloodrage, bomb, inspiration, ki pool, mental focus, mesmerist trick, phrenic pool, rage, or raging song.<br/><br/><b>Special</b><br/>A shaman or witch can use this blood hex as a standard action.",
